.Dd January 30, 2008
.Dt LOCK 9
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm lock ,
.Nm simple_lock_init ,
.Nm simple_lock ,
.Nm simple_lock_try ,
.Nm simple_unlock ,
.Nm simple_lock_freecheck ,
.Nm simple_lock_dump ,
.Nm lockinit ,
.Nm lockmgr ,
.Nm lockstatus ,
.Nm lockmgr_printinfo ,
.Nm spinlockinit ,
.Nm spinlockmgr
.Nd kernel lock functions
.Sh DESCRIPTION
These interfaces have been obsoleted and removed from the system.
.Pp
Please see the
.Xr condvar 9 ,
.Xr mutex 9 ,
and
.Xr rwlock 9
manual pages for information on kernel synchronisation primitives.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr condvar 9 ,
.Xr mutex 9 ,
.Xr rwlock 9
